### Login USER demo
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@demo.com",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

###
### Login AGENT demo
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "agent@demo.com",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

###
### Obtener info del usuario actual
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###
### Listar tickets (USER ve los suyos, AGENT ve todos)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/tickets?page=1&page_size=10&status=&priority=&search=
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###
### Crear ticket (solo USER)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Ejemplo de ticket desde .http",
  "description": "Descripción del ticket de ejemplo",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

###
### Actualizar ticket (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "priority": "MEDIUM"
}

###
### Añadir comentario a un ticket
POST http://localhost:8000/api/tickets/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "content": "Comentario de prueba desde requests.http"
}

